André Maranne https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andr%C3%A9_Maranne 0 André Maranne (born 1926) is a French former actor, best known for playing Frenchmen in English language roles in the UK from the mid-1950s. Born André Gaston Maillol, he used André Maranne as a stage name for many years.
